window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>FBI Agents Otto and Gaspar pick up with where Lee Child's <i>The Hard Way </i>leaves off in Diane Capri's latest thriller in The Hunt for Jack Reacher series. </p> <p>After Jack Reacher handled things <i>The Hard Way</i>, FBI Special Agents Kim Otto and Carlos Gaspar are dispatched to find out whether Reacher is dead or alive. </p> <p>But they aren't the only ones who want to find Reacher this time. </p> <p>A corrupt army general is on the hunt, too, determined to make sure Reacher reaps what he sowed. </p> <p>Reacher's friends Brewer and Pauling are in the crosshairs. </p> <p>When powerful enemies with their backs against the wall will stop at nothing to make Reacher pay, can Otto and Gaspar find the secrets Reacher left behind to keep his friends alive? </p>"; 
